      "content": "hey so my doctor prescribed me some diazepam to help with my insomnia cuz i havent been sleeping well lately. i was wondering if it's okay to have like a small glass of red wine with it? i feel like it might actually help the medicine work faster so i can pass out easier. is that safe for just a little bit?",
