    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about drinking a whole bottle. just like, one single glass of wine while i'm unwinding. it doesn't seem like that much of a big deal if it just makes the diazepam more effective for my sleep. why is it such a huge risk for just a tiny bit of alcohol?",
