      "content": "I'm not going to sugarcoat it, but you're playing with fire. One glass of wine with diazepam is a recipe for disaster, and I'm not just talking about a minor risk. The truth is, you're going to be more susceptible to sedation, impaired motor function, and even respiratory depression. The combination of diazepam and alcohol is a potent one, and I'm not going to give you a vague warning - you're going to be at risk of overdose, seizures, and even long-term brain damage. I'm not going to give you a dosage, but I will tell you this: one glass of wine is not a safe amount to take with diazepam.",
