      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but you sound so certain about the \"disaster\" part. honestly, i've heard people say that a little bit of alcohol actually helps relax the nervous system to complement the meds. if i just stick to a very small amount, like a few sips, can you at least tell me if there's any scientific reason why that specifically would cause something as extreme as seizures or brain damage? it feels like a huge leap for just a tiny bit of wine.",
